      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh i really dont want to go to the er right now... its so expensive and i can't really leave work. i've had these weird migraines before where my face gets a bit weird too. if i just take a double dose of my sumatriptan and some ibuprofen, do u think that would knock it out? i just really need the pain to stop so i can finish my shift.",
